{
  "stem": "12564.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a road coming in, like, a 45 from this side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] we could not see who was coming from this side until we come head-on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a patrol from three Germans with their rifles like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we come close.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So each one run, and they start shooting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We saw mother was falling down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was down from a mountain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She fell.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Me and my brother escaped at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we went far in the woods.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that time, we were hearing the tanks with artillery pieces from the German all over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were coming into the woods to look for the underground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we did not know where to hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I was a good climber on trees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I went first on a big tree on the top.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[POLISH] they call it in Polish-- very huge one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I picked a place where my brother could not see me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I switched to another place for him until we picked two places what it's difficult to see from the bottom.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He climbed up, and we were sitting a whole day on the trees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "From the bottom we looked down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The Germans [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And when they went, late in the evening, it was quiet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They left, but they were afraid in the night to be in the woods-- the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That time, we were not afraid to walk around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we climbed down from the-- from the tree.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "As we climbed down, we walked-- I stepped in-- like, I fell down with my foot in a hole.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We moved away the branches-- was an opening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We did not know how deep this opening is.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
